Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.00,0:00:06.60,Insert CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}『Thank you, my twilight』— the Pillows
Dialogue: 1,0:00:16.95,0:00:20.80,Line CN,,0,0,0,,世界必須先被毀滅 之後才能變得美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:20.80,Line EN,,0,0,0,,The world must be destroyed before it can become beautiful.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.60,0:00:22.80,Insert JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Life, Life is beautiful
Dialogue: 2,0:00:18.60,0:00:22.80,Insert CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}生命，生命如此美麗
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.55,0:00:23.48,Line CN,,0,0,0,,這是我在心中描繪的世界的願景
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.55,0:00:23.48,Line EN,,0,0,0,,This is the world I envisioned.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.34,0:00:29.45,Insert JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}僕のルーレット　回り続けてる
Dialogue: 2,0:00:23.34,0:00:29.45,Insert CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我的輪盤 會一直轉動下去
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.42,0:00:27.39,Line CN,,0,0,0,,這是世界應有的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:27.39,Line EN,,0,0,0,,This is how the world should be.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.39,0:00:29.16,Line CN,,0,0,0,,但在這個世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.39,0:00:29.16,Line EN,,0,0,0,,But in this world,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.82,0:00:31.50,Line CN,,0,0,0,,只有我的身體在腐爛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.82,0:00:31.50,Line EN,,0,0,0,,only my body is rotting --
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.02,0:00:35.31,Insert JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}She, She is wonderful
Dialogue: 2,0:00:31.02,0:00:35.31,Insert CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}她，她是這般美妙
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.19,0:00:33.76,Line CN,,0,0,0,,漸漸朽壞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.19,0:00:33.76,Line EN,,0,0,0,,becoming decayed.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.80,0:00:36.22,Line CN,,0,0,0,,沒錯 它正在朽壞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.80,0:00:36.22,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Yes, decaying.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.31,0:00:42.06,Insert JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}その瞳に今を映したい
Dialogue: 2,0:00:35.31,0:00:42.06,Insert CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}想要讓她的眼睛 映照出現在
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.33,0:00:40.06,Line CN,,0,0,0,,也許這是我原本該有的樣貌{PV原文: これが私のあるべき姿だったんのかもしれない}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.33,0:00:40.06,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Maybe this is how my body should have been.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:41.44,0:00:43.52,Line CN,,0,0,0,,也許這才是真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.44,0:00:43.52,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Maybe this is my true self.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.02,0:00:47.56,Insert JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}迷わないでもぎ取った予感を
Dialogue: 2,0:00:43.02,0:00:47.56,Insert CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}毫不猶豫抓住的預感
Dialogue: 1,0:00:49.54,0:00:52.61,Line CN,,0,0,0,,但我最後還是想起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.54,0:00:52.61,Line EN,,0,0,0,,But then finally, I remember
Dialogue: 1,0:00:49.54,0:00:56.54,Insert JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}誰かと待ち合わせてるみたいに
Dialogue: 2,0:00:49.54,0:00:56.54,Insert CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}好像在等待著誰似的
Dialogue: 1,0:00:52.61,0:00:55.47,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我還只是一個國中生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:55.47,Line EN,,0,0,0,,that I'm still only a junior high student,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.28,0:00:58.70,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我並沒思考過什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:00:58.70,Line EN,,0,0,0,,that I wasn't thinking about anything,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.54,0:01:02.18,Insert JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}見えたなら間違いじゃない
Dialogue: 2,0:00:56.54,0:01:02.18,Insert CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}如果看到就肯定不會有錯
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.62,0:01:03.22,Line CN,,0,0,0,,還有 這裡從不曾發生什麼事了不起的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:03.22,Line EN,,0,0,0,,and that nothing amazing has ever happened here.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.22,0:01:05.64,Line CN,,0,0,0,,一切都是那麼平凡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.22,0:01:05.64,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Everything is ordinary.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.37,0:01:07.78,Insert JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}キミを待ってたんだ
Dialogue: 2,0:01:04.37,0:01:07.78,Insert CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}一直在等你
