Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.98,0:03:07.88,Line CN,,0,0,0,,停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:07.88,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.88,0:03:10.85,Line CN,,0,0,0,,要我說多少次呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.88,0:03:10.85,Line EN,,0,0,0,,How many times do I have to repeat myself?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.85,0:03:14.46,Line CN,,0,0,0,,在下樓之前 先要說“早安”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:14.46,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Before you come downstairs, you got to say, "Good morning".
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.72,0:03:18.76,Line CN,,0,0,0,,好吧 再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:18.76,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Okay, why don't we give it another go?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.76,0:03:20.66,Line CN,,0,0,0,,三 二 …
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.76,0:03:20.66,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Three, two...
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.23,0:03:27.84,Line CN,,0,0,0,,酷美 親愛的 你的傲嬌人格每天都在進步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:27.84,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hidomi, sweetie, you're getting better at that tsundere personality of yours everyday.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.84,0:03:29.94,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你這樣子我可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:29.94,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I get that it's a thing you're doing,
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.94,0:03:31.54,Line CN,,0,0,0,,但我是你的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:31.54,Line EN,,0,0,0,,but I am your mother,
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.54,0:03:35.08,Line CN,,0,0,0,,不管怎樣 你還是要對我說“早安”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:35.08,Line EN,,0,0,0,,so you still have to at least say "good morning" to me.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.08,0:03:36.71,Line CN,,0,0,0,,早餐想吃什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.08,0:03:36.71,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What would you like to eat?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.71,0:03:40.18,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我可以在你的早餐裡放一點本週的特色菜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.71,0:03:40.18,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I can add some of this week's special to your usual breakfast.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.18,0:03:42.32,Line CN,,0,0,0,,看到了嗎？炒納豆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:42.32,Line EN,,0,0,0,,See? Sautéed natto.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.49,0:03:45.85,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我不想吃早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:45.85,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I don't want any.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.85,0:03:48.76,Line CN,,0,0,0,,好吧 那路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:48.76,Line EN,,0,0,0,,'Kay. Then you have a good day.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.76,0:03:51.23,Line CN,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:51.23,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.23,0:03:54.83,Line CN,,0,0,0,,在你走之前 ——三 二…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:54.83,Line EN,,0,0,0,,But before you leave -- three, two...
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.83,0:03:57.87,Line CN,,0,0,0,,早安 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:57.87,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Good morning...Mommy.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.09,0:04:24.33,Line CN,,0,0,0,,-早安！ -嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.09,0:04:24.33,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Morning! Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.33,0:04:25.83,Line CN,,0,0,0,,早安，酷美！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.33,0:04:25.83,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Hidomi!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.83,0:04:28.86,Line CN,,0,0,0,,嗯…早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.83,0:04:28.86,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm...Morning.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.86,0:04:32.93,Line CN,,0,0,0,,“你只是這麼挑逗 當然什麼也不會出來啊”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:32.93,Line EN,,0,0,0,,"Ch'yeah, well, of course nothing's gonna come out if you keep teasing it like that."
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.93,0:04:35.44,Line CN,,0,0,0,,她知道但還是繼續纏繞 轉動 迴旋 {懷疑這裡日語是furikuri furikura之類的}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:35.44,Line EN,,0,0,0,,And she knew that and kept swirling and twirling and whirling
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.44,0:04:37.47,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我宛如在天堂一般
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:37.47,Line EN,,0,0,0,,and I was in heaven for eternity, infinity,
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.47,0:04:38.97,Line CN,,0,0,0,,不要可憐我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:38.97,Line EN,,0,0,0,,no need to pity me
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.97,0:04:40.98,Line CN,,0,0,0,,喂 他沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.97,0:04:40.98,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hey, you think he's feeling all right?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.98,0:04:44.61,Line CN,,0,0,0,,井出 你就明白說昨天到底發生什麼事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:44.61,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Ide, would you just tell us what happened yesterday already?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.61,0:04:47.38,Line CN,,0,0,0,,哦吼吼 你是問我昨天嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:47.38,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Oh-ho-ho -- yesterday, you ask?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.38,0:04:49.72,Line CN,,0,0,0,,那個老師昨天在你家過夜的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:49.72,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That teacher spend the night at your place, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.72,0:04:51.39,Line CN,,0,0,0,,告訴我們到底怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:51.39,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You better tell us what happened.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.39,0:04:56.06,Line CN,,0,0,0,,有些事情需要留下想像的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:56.06,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You guys, some things ought to be left to the imagination.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.46,0:04:59.86,Line CN,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:04:59.86,Line EN,,0,0,0,,For reals?! Seriously?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.86,0:05:03.14,Line CN,,0,0,0,,天啊 恭喜恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:03.14,Line EN,,0,0,0,,No, way. Oh, my gosh. Congratulations.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.14,0:05:04.87,Line CN,,0,0,0,,那當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:04.87,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah...
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.87,0:05:05.97,Line CN,,0,0,0,,說真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:05.97,Line EN,,0,0,0,,For reals?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.97,0:05:09.47,Line CN,,0,0,0,,還有 你昨天說的那個秘密計劃是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:09.47,Line EN,,0,0,0,,By the way, what was the secret plan you were talking about yesterday?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.47,0:05:12.44,Line CN,,0,0,0,,那個嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:12.44,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, that?
