Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.67,0:08:31.07,Line CN,,0,0,0,,-你真壞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:31.07,Line EN,,0,0,0,,-You're so bad.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.07,0:08:32.84,Line CN,,0,0,0,,-老師 我  -你會害我惹上麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:32.84,Line EN,,0,0,0,,-Teacher, I -- -You're gonna get me in trouble.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.84,0:08:34.88,Line CN,,0,0,0,,-我忍不住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:34.88,Line EN,,0,0,0,,-I can't help myself.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.88,0:08:37.61,Line CN,,0,0,0,,-看看你對我做的 -老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:37.61,Line EN,,0,0,0,,-Look what you're doing to me. -Teacher!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.88,0:08:40.65,Line CN,,0,0,0,,-老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.88,0:08:40.65,Line EN,,0,0,0,,-Oh, Teacher! Oh!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.65,0:08:42.95,Line CN,,0,0,0,,什麼鬼？她在給她看什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.65,0:08:42.95,Line EN,,0,0,0,,The hell? What is she making her watch?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.95,0:08:46.62,Line CN,,0,0,0,,聽起來很糟糕 非常糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.95,0:08:46.62,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Whatever it is it sounds naughty -- real naughty.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.62,0:08:49.29,Line CN,,0,0,0,,下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.62,0:08:49.29,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Next.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.00,0:08:55.73,Line CN,,0,0,0,,下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:55.73,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Next.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.50,0:09:02.60,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你怎麼一點點反應都沒有？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:02.60,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Would it kill you to have even the tiniest reaction to this?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.60,0:09:06.04,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你是想等到自己花都謝了再進入青春期嗎？{line join}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:06.04,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You don't want to wait until you're over the hill to hit adolescence, do you?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.04,0:09:09.84,Line CN,,0,0,0,,好吧 到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:09.84,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Fine. I've seen all I need to.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.84,0:09:12.55,Line CN,,0,0,0,,-你們誰是下一個？-我！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:12.55,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Which one of you is next? I am!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.55,0:09:14.98,Line CN,,0,0,0,,呃 井出你用不著測試
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:14.98,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Eh, I don't need to test you, Ide.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.98,0:09:16.92,Line CN,,0,0,0,,除了他還有誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:16.92,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who's next besides him?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.92,0:09:19.57,Line CN,,0,0,0,,-我 我！-森 待會告訴我們你看了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:19.56,Line EN,,0,0,0,,-Oh! Oh! Me! -Mori, tell us what you see!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.57,0:09:21.20,Line CN,,0,0,0,,恐怕不行 我聽說你必須自己看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:21.21,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I don't think I can. I hear you have to see for yourselves.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.27,0:09:23.62,Line CN,,0,0,0,,真無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:23.17,Line CN - Top,,0,0,0,,-我試過了 -好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:23.62,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.27,0:09:23.17,Line EN - Top,,0,0,0,,-I tried! -Nasty!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.62,0:09:26.09,Line CN,,0,0,0,,是…是什麼？蔬菜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:26.09,Line EN,,0,0,0,,W-W-What is it? Vegetables.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.85,0:09:53.02,Line CN,,0,0,0,,嘿 公主小姐 可以給我一張餐巾嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:53.02,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hey, princess, could I get a napkin, please?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.02,0:09:55.89,Line CN,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我的酪梨帕菲好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.02,0:09:55.89,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but is my avocado parfait ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.89,0:10:00.00,Line CN,,0,0,0,,酷美醬 請幫我咖啡續杯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.89,0:10:00.00,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hidomi-chan, more coffee, please?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.23,0:10:03.66,Line CN,,0,0,0,,她那種態度真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:03.66,Line EN,,0,0,0,,She's at her best when she gives us attitude like that.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.66,0:10:08.10,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我就喜歡她用責罵的眼神俯視我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:08.10,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I just love it when she looks down on us with those judgy eyes.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.10,0:10:11.54,Line CN,,0,0,0,,同感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:11.54,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.54,0:10:13.71,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你做得棒極了 公主小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:13.71,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You're on fire, princess.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.71,0:10:16.00,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你真的很有潛力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:16.00,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You have what it takes to be a champ, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.88,0:10:19.98,Line CN,,0,0,0,,謝謝你來店裡幫我 酷美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:19.98,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Thanks for helping out, Hidomi, sweetie.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.98,0:10:21.52,Line CN,,0,0,0,,幫了大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.98,0:10:21.52,Line EN,,0,0,0,,It really needed it today.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.52,0:10:22.92,Line CN,,0,0,0,,唔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:22.92,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.90,0:10:24.75,Line CN,,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:24.75,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That said,
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.75,0:10:27.14,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我真的應該抓緊考慮僱人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:27.14,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I should probably look into hiring someone soon.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.16,0:10:31.92,Line CN,,0,0,0,,不能因為咖啡店的事情耽誤你的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:31.92,Line EN,,0,0,0,,We can't have you wasting your valuable time helping me out at the café.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.27,0:10:42.10,Line CN,,0,0,0,,這裡的工廠看起來和那一個一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.27,0:10:42.10,Line EN,,0,0,0,,The Plant here looks just like the other one.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.80,0:10:44.94,Line CN,,0,0,0,,發出的聲音也是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.80,0:10:44.94,Line EN,,0,0,0,,It makes the same sound, too.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.01,0:10:49.30,Line CN,,0,0,0,,他現在在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.01,0:10:49.30,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I wonder where he is right now.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.65,0:10:59.39,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我最近開始覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:10:59.39,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking --
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.39,0:11:02.01,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我們是不是不要再等他了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.39,0:11:02.01,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's time we stopped waiting for him.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.06,0:11:04.79,Line CN,,0,0,0,,也許我們應該向前看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.06,0:11:04.79,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's time for us to move on.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.33,0:11:10.56,Line CN,,0,0,0,,對不起 我不該說這些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:10.56,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I shouldn't say things like this.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.56,0:11:12.30,Line CN,,0,0,0,,但是你——
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:12.30,Line EN,,0,0,0,,But now you're --
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.30,0:11:14.70,Line CN,,0,0,0,,媽媽 我——
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:14.70,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Mommy, you know what?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.70,0:11:15.62,Line CN,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,0:11:15.62,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.29,0:11:32.80,Line CN,,0,0,0,,酷美！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:32.80,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hidomi!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.69,0:11:35.49,Line CN,,0,0,0,,剛才真是千鈞一髮呢 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:35.49,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That was a close one, ma'am.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.49,0:11:36.84,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我向您道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.49,0:11:36.84,Line EN,,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.29,0:11:41.26,Line CN,,0,0,0,,要是再遲一點 她就要溢出了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.29,0:11:41.26,Line EN,,0,0,0,,A little bit more, and she would've overflowed.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.26,0:11:43.32,Line CN,,0,0,0,,溢出？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:43.32,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Overflowed?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.66,0:11:47.05,Line CN,,0,0,0,,奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.66,0:11:47.05,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.07,0:11:49.60,Line CN,,0,0,0,,-剛才的撞擊應該致命才對 -致命?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.07,0:11:49.60,Line EN,,0,0,0,,-I was sure it was a fatal hit. -Fatal hit?!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.60,0:11:51.76,Line CN,,0,0,0,,很不幸 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:51.76,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, ma'am...
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.51,0:11:53.91,Line CN,,0,0,0,,您的女兒平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.51,0:11:53.91,Line EN,,0,0,0,,your daughter is going to be fine.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.91,0:11:55.50,Line CN,,0,0,0,,很不幸？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.91,0:11:55.50,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That's unfortunate?!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.49,0:11:56.92,Line CN,,0,0,0,,酷美 親愛的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:11:56.92,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hidomi, dear!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.08,0:11:59.31,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你還好嗎？受傷了沒有？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:11:59.31,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.78,0:12:04.19,Line CN,,0,0,0,,喂！那是我的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:04.19,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's mine!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.19,0:12:06.15,Line CN,,0,0,0,,沒有在放音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.19,0:12:06.15,Line EN,,0,0,0,,It's not even playing anything.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.15,0:12:07.01,Line CN,,0,0,0,,還給我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.15,0:12:07.01,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.36,0:12:13.03,Line CN,,0,0,0,,這是哪裡來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:13.03,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Where did you get this?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.03,0:12:17.16,Line CN,,0,0,0,,這不是在大街上隨隨便便就能買到的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:17.16,Line EN,,0,0,0,,It's not something anyone can just walk off the street and buy.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.16,0:12:21.57,Line CN,,0,0,0,,-這是… -嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.16,0:12:21.57,Line EN,,0,0,0,,-This is just... -Hmm?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.57,0:12:23.17,Line CN,,0,0,0,,這是有人送給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:23.17,Line EN,,0,0,0,,It was a gift.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.17,0:12:24.87,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你不應該戴著這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:24.87,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I don't think you should wear them.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.87,0:12:25.96,Line CN,,0,0,0,,這個不適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:25.96,Line EN,,0,0,0,,They don't suit you.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.84,0:12:29.98,Line CN,,0,0,0,,假裝自己聽不見——
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.84,0:12:29.98,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Pretending you can't hear --
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.98,0:12:32.31,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你喜歡這樣 對嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:32.31,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That's, like, your thing, am I right?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.31,0:12:34.88,Line CN,,0,0,0,,當你對這個世界按下了暫停鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:34.88,Line EN,,0,0,0,,When you hit pause on the world like that,
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.88,0:12:37.82,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你的身體也會漸漸開始腐壞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:37.82,Line EN,,0,0,0,,your body will slowly start to rot away.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.82,0:12:39.84,Line CN,,0,0,0,,這是你所希望的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:39.84,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Is that what you want to happen to you?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.60,0:12:50.43,Line CN,,0,0,0,,請 請等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:50.43,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute! You there!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.43,0:12:53.20,Line CN,,0,0,0,,夫人 您的女兒沒有死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.43,0:12:53.20,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Just so you know, I take full responsibility
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.20,0:12:56.54,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我會承擔全部責任的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:56.54,Line EN,,0,0,0,,for your daughter hanging on to her life.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.54,0:12:57.86,Line CN,,0,0,0,,對了 還有一件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:57.86,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, and by the way...
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.96,0:13:02.89,Line CN,,0,0,0,,當心騎著 Vespa 的女人 {line join}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:02.89,Line EN,,0,0,0,,careful of the woman on the Vespa -- for your own good.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.41,0:13:09.78,Line CN,,0,0,0,,酷美！記下她的車牌號了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.41,0:13:09.78,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hidomi! Her plates! Did you get them?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.78,0:13:11.19,Line CN,,0,0,0,,肇事逃逸！肇事逃逸！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:11.19,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hit-and-run! Hit-and-run!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.19,0:13:13.92,Line CN,,0,0,0,,千萬不要變成這樣不負責任的大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:13.92,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Never be an irresponsible adult like that!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.92,0:13:16.26,Line CN,,0,0,0,,她是誰？她怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:16.26,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Who is she? What's with her?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.26,0:13:19.40,Line CN,,0,0,0,,不知道 但是她有點帥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.26,0:13:19.40,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but you got to admit she sure was cool.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.40,0:13:21.58,Line CN,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:21.58,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Heh...
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.10,0:13:28.94,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我對自己毫無期待
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:28.94,Line EN,,0,0,0,,There is nothing I want to be.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.84,0:13:31.88,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我什麼事情都不想做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.84,0:13:31.88,Line EN,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I want to do.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.11,0:13:36.22,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我甚至不知道自己想成為什麼樣子的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:36.22,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I don't even have an image of what I want to be.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.64,0:13:37.96,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我什麼都沒有{PV原文:私には何もない}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.64,0:13:37.96,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I have nothing.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.71,0:13:41.98,Line CN,,0,0,0,,有的只是…無
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:41.98,Line EN,,0,0,0,,All that exists...is zero.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.01,0:14:07.30,Line CN,,0,0,0,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:07.30,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.98,0:14:14.98,Line CN,,0,0,0,,酷美？親愛的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:14.98,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hidomi? Sweetie?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.98,0:14:16.80,Line CN,,0,0,0,,-媽媽！-酷美！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:16.80,Line EN,,0,0,0,,-Mom! Mama! -Hidomi!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.98,0:14:49.65,Line CN,,0,0,0,,雲雀…弄？呃 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:49.65,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hiba...ji-jiri? Oh, I --
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.65,0:14:53.22,Line CN,,0,0,0,,是你嗎 井出？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:53.22,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Is that you, I-I-Ide?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.26,0:15:00.41,Line CN,,0,0,0,,它開始行動了 但這是哪一個？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.26,0:15:00.41,Line EN,,0,0,0,,It's started to move, but which is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.30,0:15:05.03,Line CN,,0,0,0,,-那個是什麼鬼東西？-天曉得！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:05.03,Line EN,,0,0,0,,-What the heck is that thing? -I have no idea!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.03,0:15:07.30,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我在回家的路上 然後——
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:07.30,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I was just walking home, and then --
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.30,0:15:09.87,Line CN,,0,0,0,,-你這麼晚還在外面？-呃 我有事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:09.87,Line EN,,0,0,0,,-You were out this late? -Uh, I had stuff to do,
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.87,0:15:11.17,Line CN,,0,0,0,,然後那個東西就突然出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.87,0:15:11.17,Line EN,,0,0,0,,and that thing just suddenly appeared.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.17,0:15:12.98,Line CN,,0,0,0,,好吧 但是從哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.17,0:15:12.98,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but from where?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.41,0:15:16.51,Line CN,,0,0,0,,呃 好像是從我的腦袋裡出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:16.51,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Well, it was like from my head.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.72,0:15:25.10,Line CN,,0,0,0,,好像甩掉它了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:25.10,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I think we lost it.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.04,0:15:46.82,Line CN,,0,0,0,,可惡 到底怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:46.82,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Holy shit! What the hell's going on?!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.72,0:15:50.72,Line CN,,0,0,0,,別過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:50.72,Line EN,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.28,0:17:07.59,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我明白了 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:07.59,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I see now. That's how it is, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.13,0:17:15.30,Line CN,,0,0,0,,喂！她人在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:15.30,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where is she --
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.30,0:17:17.04,Line CN,,0,0,0,,把那個東西從你身體裡拉出來的傢伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:17.04,Line EN,,0,0,0,,the one who pulled that out of you?!
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.27,0:17:21.30,Line CN,,0,0,0,,回答我！你被撞了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.27,0:17:21.30,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Answer me! You were hit, weren't you?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.30,0:17:23.97,Line CN,,0,0,0,,是不是一個騎著 Vespa 的女人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.30,0:17:23.97,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Was it a woman on a Vespa?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.97,0:17:26.24,Line CN,,0,0,0,,Ves...pa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.97,0:17:26.24,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Ves...pa?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.88,0:17:30.94,Line CN,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:30.94,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.21,0:17:35.80,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你是誰？井出他沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:35.80,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Who are you? And Ide...is he okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.45,0:17:40.45,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我會儘量給他治療的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:40.45,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do what I can for his wounds.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.45,0:17:43.56,Line CN,,0,0,0,,-你回家吧 -等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:43.56,Line EN,,0,0,0,,-You get home safe, okay? -Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.56,0:17:45.08,Line CN,,0,0,0,,順帶一提
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:45.08,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way,
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.66,0:17:49.68,Line CN,,0,0,0,,那個很適合你 讚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:49.68,Line EN,,0,0,0,,that thing looks good on you. Nice.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.01,0:18:22.34,Insert CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}『Little Busters』— the Pillows
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.16,0:18:22.56,Line CN,,0,0,0,,嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:22.56,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.56,0:18:25.17,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你沒有受傷真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:25.17,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm so glad nothing actually happened to you,
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.17,0:18:26.77,Line CN,,0,0,0,,酷美 親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.17,0:18:26.77,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hidomi, dear.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.77,0:18:27.80,Line CN,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:27.80,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.17,0:18:31.31,Line CN,,0,0,0,,媽媽可擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:31.31,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You know, Mommy was so worried
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.31,0:18:33.70,Line CN,,0,0,0,,以為你要離家出走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:33.70,Line EN,,0,0,0,,that maybe you decided to run away from home.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.68,0:18:35.31,Insert JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}With the kids sing out the future
Dialogue: 2,0:18:31.68,0:18:35.31,Insert CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}孩子們歌唱著未來
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.31,0:18:39.08,Insert JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Maybe, kids don't need the masters
Dialogue: 2,0:18:35.31,0:18:39.08,Insert CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}也許孩子們不需要主人
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.54,0:18:38.35,Line CN,,0,0,0,,但是如果真的要離家出走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.54,0:18:38.35,Line EN,,0,0,0,,But if youwere going to run away,
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.35,0:18:39.81,Line CN,,0,0,0,,一定要搞得轟轟烈烈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:39.81,Line EN,,0,0,0,,you should do it with a bang.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.08,0:18:46.85,Insert JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Just waiting for the little busters
Dialogue: 2,0:18:39.08,0:18:46.85,Insert CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}只要等小混蛋們到來
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.81,0:18:42.08,Line CN,,0,0,0,,但是千萬別把房子給砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:42.08,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Just please try not to break the house next time,
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.08,0:18:44.12,Line CN,,0,0,0,,好嗎？-嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:44.12,Line EN,,0,0,0,,all right, sweetie. -Mm.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.71,0:18:53.63,Line CN,,0,0,0,,這——這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:53.63,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Bu-- But why?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.63,0:18:56.36,Line CN,,0,0,0,,她想要為昨天的事情負責
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.63,0:18:56.36,Line EN,,0,0,0,,She's taking responsibility for yesterday.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.36,0:18:57.56,Line CN,,0,0,0,,自我介紹一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:57.56,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Please introduce yourself.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.13,0:19:00.80,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我是仁由{じんゆ 求助}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:00.80,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I'm Jinyu.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.37,0:19:08.61,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我靠！那些繃帶是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:08.61,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Whoa! What's with all those bandages?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.61,0:19:11.00,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了井出？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.61,0:19:11.00,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what happened to you, Ide?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.00,0:19:14.08,Line CN,,0,0,0,,不知道該怎麼跟你們說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:14.08,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Man, I don't even know where to start.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.08,0:19:16.65,Line CN,,0,0,0,,發生了很多 很多事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:16.65,Line EN,,0,0,0,,A lot of stuff happened, quite a lot of stuff.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.94,0:19:18.19,Line CN,,0,0,0,,“很多事”？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:18.19,Line EN,,0,0,0,,"A lot of stuff"?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.19,0:19:19.59,Line CN,,0,0,0,,那算什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.19,0:19:19.59,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What kind of answer is that?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.59,0:19:21.64,Line CN,,0,0,0,,這跟沒說有什麼區別
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:21.64,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That's like a non-answer answer.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.53,0:19:36.37,Line CN,,0,0,0,,在你們開始合理又災難性的新的一天之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:36.37,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Today, as you start on your understandably
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.37,0:19:38.14,Line CN,,0,0,0,,時下的少年少女們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.37,0:19:38.14,Line EN,,0,0,0,,disastrous day as modern-day youth,
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.14,0:19:40.67,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我作為現實生活中決定性的贏家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:40.67,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I, as someone who is the clear winner in life structurally,
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.67,0:19:42.78,Line CN,,0,0,0,,要告訴你們很重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:42.78,Line EN,,0,0,0,,would like to present to you something very important --
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.78,0:19:45.01,Line CN,,0,0,0,,關於如何在這個世界上生存
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:45.01,Line EN,,0,0,0,,the "this and that" on how to live in this universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:49.37,Rect,,0,0,0,,{\fscx950\fscy1100\alpha30\blur10\pos(192,237.6)}■
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.03,0:19:49.37,Text,,0,0,0,,\h                    B班（23）\NU.Beviaqua: 話說 Takeshi 是不是\N\h                          喜歡 Emily？\NKAs: 真的嗎？！\NAkihiro: 真的是這樣嗎？！\NSt: 我都不知道！！\NRYO: 現在已經 Free 了吧？\NU.Beviaqua: 機會！！\NKAs: 機——會！！\NAkihiro: 加油！！\NU.Beviaqua: 過了這個村就沒了這個店！\NU.Beviaqua: 可不能放過這次機會\NTK: 欸？\NTK: 這是在說我嗎？\NU.Beviaqua: 會去的吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.01,0:19:46.38,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你們會被測試
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:46.38,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You will be tested on it,
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.38,0:19:48.45,Line CN,,0,0,0,,甚至每天的生活本身就是測試
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.38,0:19:48.45,Line EN,,0,0,0,,insomuch as every day in itself is a test.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.45,0:19:50.62,Line CN,,0,0,0,,-對 就是你 - 呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:50.62,Line EN,,0,0,0,,-Yes. You over there. -Uh...
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.62,0:19:52.29,Line CN,,0,0,0,,回答錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:52.29,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Wrong answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:20:04.25,Rect,,0,0,0,,{\fscx950\fscy1400\alpha30\blur10\pos(193.6,290.4)}■
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.00,0:20:04.25,Text,,0,0,0,,\h                    B班（23）\NU.Beviaqua: 反正 Free 了\NTK: 蛤？\NAkihiro: 是的 因為 Free 了\N安東: Free!\NTK: 喂 等等\NU.Beviaqua: 你是不會做出不好好利用\N\h                          Free 的那種沒勁事吧？\N安東: 那麼——Take 醬怎麼做？\NTK: 你們這些人\NU.Beviaqua: 只能利用好 Free 了！\NAkihiro: 好好利用吧！！\N安東: 這樣美味的 Free 可是很難得的哦！\NKAs: 同意\N安東: Free 好啊，Free 真是好！\NU.Beviaqua: Freefree 喔 Freefree\NKAs: Furifuri\NAkihiro: Furifuri?\N安東: Furikuri?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.29,0:19:54.09,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我最近想明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:54.09,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I figured out something recently.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.09,0:19:55.69,Line CN,,0,0,0,,與其為了隨機的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.09,0:19:55.69,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Instead of preparing a concrete answer
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.69,0:19:57.52,Line CN,,0,0,0,,準備具體的答案 我認為
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:57.52,Line EN,,0,0,0,,to random questions, I have come to the conclusion
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.52,0:19:59.23,Line CN,,0,0,0,,並不存在你們的生存之道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:19:59.23,Line EN,,0,0,0,,that there is no real way to live,
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.23,0:20:00.94,Line CN,,0,0,0,,對於你們這些只要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:00.94,Line EN,,0,0,0,,not for those of you who exist contently
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.94,0:20:04.10,Line CN,,0,0,0,,蠢動著動物般的性慾就能獲得滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.94,0:20:04.10,Line EN,,0,0,0,,by only jerking your animalistic sexual urges to fulfillment,
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.10,0:20:07.00,Line CN,,0,0,0,,在我們眼裡一無是處的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:07.00,Line EN,,0,0,0,,and you who have absolutely no skill to convince us otherwise.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.00,0:20:09.70,Line CN - Top,,0,0,0,,我付出了那麼多 但是成果少得可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:09.70,Line EN - Top,,0,0,0,,I gave so, so much, but there was very little output.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.70,0:20:12.91,Line CN - Top,,0,0,0,,微不足道隻能供人玩樂的小蟲子對我毫無價值
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:12.91,Line EN - Top,,0,0,0,,I have no use for the tiny pieces of scum bugs that have been toyed with.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.90,0:20:12.86,Line CN,,950,0,0,,Furi…kuri…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.90,0:20:12.86,Line EN,,950,0,0,,Fooly...Cooly...
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.96,0:20:17.71,Line CN,,0,0,0,,聽你們老師一言 我不希望你們成為不存在的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:17.71,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Listen to your teacher. I have no desire for all of you to wind up as nonexistent youth.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.71,0:20:21.62,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我要讓你們都變成宇宙級別的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:21.62,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What I want is for all of you to become adults on a cosmological scale!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.56,0:20:27.17,Rect,,0,0,0,,{\fscx700\fscy1200\alpha30\blur10\pos(168,252)}■
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.56,0:20:27.17,Text,,0,0,0,,\h                    B班（23）\Nmi-: FuriKuri\Nichiro-: furi Kuri\Nkanako: Furi Kuri！！？\Ndaidai: FLCL\Nkome: FuriKuri\N竹尾: furikuri\N(^o^): FL--CL--\Nwa: FuriKuri\NASADA: f l c l！\Noshiyama: Furi！Kuri！\Nsada: FLCLFLCLFLCL\NKUBO: Furi Kuri！\Nkiyo: Furi Kuri！！\Narai: FLCL！！\N（FLCL的假名和英文洗刷版）
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.62,0:20:24.05,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你不需要翅膀也能在宇宙探險
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:24.05,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You don't need wings to go venture out into the universe.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.05,0:20:26.52,Line CN,,0,0,0,,誰會需要長翅膀的四輪汽車？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:26.52,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Who would ride a four-wheeled car with wings, anyway?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.52,0:20:28.59,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你們不可以變成那樣的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:28.59,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You must not become that kind of adult.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.59,0:20:31.36,Line CN,,0,0,0,,明白了嗎？你們不需要四個輪子！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.59,0:20:31.36,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Do you understand me? You do not need four wheels!
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.36,0:20:34.70,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你們只需要兩個——就像池塘裡的底棲魚一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.36,0:20:34.70,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You only need two -- like a bottom-feeding fish in a pond,
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.70,0:20:36.73,Line CN,,0,0,0,,在低垂的柳樹下面聚成一群
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:42.59,TopLeft,,0,0,0,,Furi Kuri 和 FLCL 的洗刷版
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.70,0:20:36.73,Line EN,,0,0,0,,gathering underneath a weeping willow tree.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.73,0:20:38.77,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你們的下方有強大的重力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.73,0:20:38.77,Line EN,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of gravity underneath all of you...
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.67,0:20:46.32,Line CN,,0,0,0,,所以站起來！你們就越差強人意越好 最好變成一團糟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:46.32,Line EN,,0,0,0,,...so stand up! Be as adequate as you can, a complete mess,
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.32,0:20:48.79,Line CN,,0,0,0,,生來注定平庸！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:48.79,Line EN,,0,0,0,,born to be mild!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.40,0:21:14.90,Line CN,,0,0,0,,這就對了 我想要的終於要出現了 {PV原文:ようやくほんめい登場だぜ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:14.90,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That's right, the real one's finally appearing.
Comment: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{『Spiky Seeds』 - the Pillows  新歌還沒有歌詞，鴿了}
